            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the leeks have softened, add the <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>flour</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Add the<strong> vegetable stock, chopped potatoes </strong>and the<strong> single soya</strong> and cook for 15-18 min or until the potatoes are almost fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
