          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>haddock bites </strong>and <strong>spinach</strong> to the potatoes and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 4-5 min or until the haddock is cooked through and the potatoes are fork-tender – this is your <strong>dairy-free</strong> <strong>curried haddock, leek & potato chowder</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
